metadata.name: 2 is better than 1
metadata.description:
From a distance I saw this mother and calf cuddling with each other and my excitement was real! I’ve captured a lot of single Teddycows, but getting a good shot of 2 is super hard. So I slowly approached them with the intention to not disturb them in their morning cuddle. I witnessed the preciousness for a few minutes and I was hoping for exactly what I captured in this image. A mother and a calf looking straight into my lens, while standing together in the field!

Artist: Nick Bng  
Edition: 1/1 NFT
